    <item>
      <title>阿提哈德报告称，网络增长带来的利润增长了五倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/etihad-reports-five-fold-increase-in-profit-on-network-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿提哈德航空 PJSC 报告称，随着这家总部位于阿布扎比的航空公司扩大其网络以满足不断增长的旅行需求，其利润增长了五倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/etihad-reports-five-fold-increase-in-profit-on-network-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及大幅加息后货币贬值超过35%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-unexpectedly-hikes-interest-rate-to-27-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及提高了利率，并允许其货币贬值超过35%，这是期待已久的贬值，这可能为国际货币基金组织增加数十亿美元的贷款铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-unexpectedly-hikes-interest-rate-to-27-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 07:29:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
